---
title: Indonesian-Inspired Peanut Satay Chicken Burgers with Chili-Garlic Wedges and Caramelized Pineapple
description: Indonesian-inspired chicken burgers are gussied up with chili-garlic sauce and cilantro for maximum flavour! Our creamy peanut satay sauce adds a nutty profile and plays well with the caramelized pineapple. Wedges get a little love too with a drizzle of pungent chili-garlic sauce, a squeeze of mayo and a sprinkle of crispy shallots!
